definitions.definition: A hanging , usually of rich stuff, at the back of a throne , altar , etc.
Any of the longitudinal series of plates that encircle the body, excluding the ventral scales .
A sound produced using the dorsum of the tongue .

main_definition: ( art ) A hanging , usually of rich stuff, at the back of a throne , altar , etc.
secondary_definitions: ( zootomy , in snakes ) Any of the longitudinal series of plates that encircle the body, excluding the ventral scales .
( linguistics ) A sound produced using the dorsum of the tongue .
